title: Adventures of Sherlock Holmes
description:
12 x 45 minutes


Twelve Sherlock Holmes dramas with the excellent combo of Clive Merrison as Holmes and the late Michael Williams as Dr Watson. The stories are:

1 - A Scandal In Bohemia

2 - The Red Headed League

3 - A Case of Identity

4 - The Boscombe Valley Mystery

5 - The Five Orange Pips

6 - The Man With the Twisted Lip

7 - The Blue Carbuncle

8 - The Speckled Band

9 - The Engineer's Thumb

10 - The Noble Bachelor

11 - The Beryl Coronet

12 - The Copper Beeches
